data.title: Select Tile
data.content:
<form>
  Select Tile:
<input type="hidden" id="dialog-redirect" name="goto" />
  <button type="button" onclick="$('#dialog-redirect').val('statue');">Statue</button>
  <button type="button" onclick="$('#dialog-redirect').val('activestatue');">Active - Statue</button>
  <button type="button" onclick="$('#dialog-redirect').val('activeplatform');">Active - Platform</button>
  <button type="button" onclick="$('#dialog-redirect').val('platform');">Empty Platform</button>
</form>
